        "created_at": "2019-12-22T14:14:12.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p><strong>1979 Ch\u00e2teau Mouton Rothschild</strong> <em>- France, Bordeaux, M\u00e9doc, Pauillac (12/14/2019)</em></p>\n<p>Complex and exciting on the nose with spice, soil and cedar. On the palate supple, elegant and balanced with sweet juicy fruit, tobacco and some earth. Not very long and powerful but enjoyable and a pleasant surprise!! <em><strong>(92 pts.)</strong></em></p>\n<p><em>Posted from <a href=\"https://www.cellartracker.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">CellarTracker</a></em></p>",
