        "created_at": "2019-12-24T14:53:19.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Was at a bacchanal lunch a few months ago where I was able to compare this to a \u201879 BV GdL I had brought.  The Mouton was unfortunately very much past it\u2019s prime.  The BV was drinking wonderfully.  YMMV, of course.</p>",
